      "text": "Looking back on the 6202 Journey, there were prolonged moments of discomfort.  Dense writing.  Mathematical concepts.  Thickets of ideas.  How do I avoid only a surface understanding of what I have encountered?  Reading the insights of our peers helped immensely.  Oh!, that's what a Markovian Moment, or Blanket or Lambda something means to you. Each of those explorations added to my understanding.  I was not alone.  I never was.  I had peers, guides, authors, thinkers and my lived experience to draw upon.  "
